description: We're thrilled to have this stud back.Yes, that's right, Shawn has paid us another visit-- and he's looking better than ever. We had a lot of requests to see more of him, and we decided to let him put on another show for us. He's been hard at work, still in his first year of college, and still playing in his band. You can tell he's been working out and running a lot... he's more defined now. At 5'9', he packs on a lot of lean muscle for his frame. We think he looks great. And we're sure you're going to like how he looks too.
title: Shawn
